      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:400;color:#191817;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Selling in Burbank 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(25,24,23,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Burbank's tightly held acreage holdings, Bulimba Creek bushland frontage and equestrian character attract a specific lifestyle buyer pool from across south-east Queensland. Here is what sellers need to know in 2026.
      </p>
